Title: A Nurturing Environment
Description:
Young whelps can be careless in how they treat their space. The daycare is effectively under siege day in and day out!

Help clean up the daycare. The new whelps will need a proper place to stay.

I will not let one claw set down on unpolished stone or overgrown grass!
ObjectivesText: Help put the Little Scales Daycare back into order.
